==Description==

The tool [[Image:CAM_Stop.svg|24px]] [[CAM_Stop|Stop]] inserts a Stop command (M1). This command will Pause a running program on the CNC controller, waiting for user interaction to continue.

'''Note: this does not stop the spindle.'''

==Usage==

# Press the {{KEY|[[Image:CAM_Stop.svg|16px]] [[CAM_Stop|Stop]]}} button

==Properties==

* {{PropertyData|Stop}}: Defines if the Stop is optional or mandatory.


